latestPosts.caption:
I haven't been actively working on my chopping block series so I'm not sure if I updated you on my thoughts on the @dominiquecosmetics Essential palette. I ended up decluttering it not because I didn't love the color story or formula, but because I don't wear eyeshadow every day anymore and I don't want to have a collection of 30 palettes. This palette is super pretty but the shimmers aren't anything special. I have these shades in other palettes that I know I'll reach for more often. 

I'm sorry for my lack of posting, currently finishing up my masters degree and I'm super busy and exhausted. I'm also trying to figure things out and deal with the uncertainty of what comes next. I finish my internship at the high school this week (2 days left) + I'll have 1 day left of training next week. I have 1 online class left this week and next week we're going out to brunch for our last class. I have 1 assignment left to review & submit and 1 assignment to do (just did the title page lol). 

How have you been? Anything new in your life?

*sent in pr

Long Beach Iced Tea - earthy rosy pink
